Comment: 0,0:00:15.91,0:00:15.91,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,OP-JP
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.20,0:21:42.99,OP-JP,,20,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Yeah, it was nice to meet you and everything
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.41,0:21:45.03,OP-JP,,20,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}But there are somethings you should know
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.99,0:21:48.33,OP-JP,,20,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I'm not like those other girls you're used to
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.12,0:21:50.91,OP-JP,,20,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}If you think you have what it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.41,0:21:52.62,OP-JP,,20,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Then I'll be right here
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.79,0:21:57.30,OP-JP,,20,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I've been all alone for so long
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.46,0:22:00.97,OP-JP,,20,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Think I'm better off just on my own
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.17,0:22:04.68,OP-JP,,20,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}When you're looking for love, it's always hiding away
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.68,0:22:08.10,OP-JP,,20,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I know how boys just love to play their games
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.52,0:22:09.72,OP-JP,,20,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}They say love is blind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.72,0:22:11.60,OP-JP,,20,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}閉じない eyes, 握って tight
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.60,0:22:12.69,OP-JP,,20,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Enjoy the ride
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.69,0:22:14.35,OP-JP,,20,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I'm not easy, it's not hard
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.35,0:22:16.40,OP-JP,,20,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Just give a girl 全て world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.40,0:22:20.15,OP-JP,,20,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}何も言わなくても Your eyes are saying
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.15,0:22:24.45,OP-JP,,20,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}All that I need to know from you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.45,0:22:27.95,OP-JP,,20,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I know all of the baggage and burdens you carry beside you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.16,0:22:31.45,OP-JP,,20,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}There's a beauty in taking a chance and letting it guide you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.08,0:22:33.96,OP-JP,,20,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Look inside the crystal
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.96,0:22:36.79,OP-JP,,20,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}There's no answers, no map, no guide
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.79,0:22:37.92,OP-JP,,20,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Follow what you feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.80,0:22:42.26,OP-JP,,20,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}No, I don't chase, I don't play hide and seek
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.51,0:22:44.80,OP-JP,,20,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}本気なら見せてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.80,0:22:46.39,OP-JP,,20,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Come find me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.39,0:22:48.01,OP-JP,,20,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}"Girl be mine"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.01,0:22:49.89,OP-JP,,20,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}なんて信じない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.89,0:22:53.31,OP-JP,,20,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Gotta show me boy 秘密はナシだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.31,0:22:56.81,OP-JP,,20,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Yesterday the stars aligned our way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.81,0:23:00.23,OP-JP,,20,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Today I know I've been running around your brain
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.23,0:23:02.15,OP-JP,,20,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I want roses, no red flags
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.15,0:23:04.20,OP-JP,,20,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Gonna say さよなら Bye bye
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.28,0:23:04.78,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\3c&HE8BC85&}I'm not afraid to throw it all away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.78,0:23:05.24,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\3c&HB495FE&}I'm not afraid to throw it all away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.24,0:23:05.49,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\3c&HE8BC85&}I'm not afraid to throw it all away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.49,0:23:06.95,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\an8\3c&HB495FE&}I'm not afraid to throw it all away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.95,0:23:07.57,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\an8\3c&HB495FE&}Think twice about it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.57,0:23:08.33,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\an8}Think twice about it
Comment: 0,0:00:15.91,0:00:15.91,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,OP-CN
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.20,0:21:42.99,OP-CN,,0,20,0,,{\fad(300,300)}是啊  能够遇见你确实很幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.41,0:21:45.03,OP-CN,,0,20,0,,{\fad(300,300)}但有些事你得搞清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.99,0:21:48.33,OP-CN,,0,20,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我可不像你习惯接触的那些女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.12,0:21:50.91,OP-CN,,0,20,0,,{\fad(300,300)}如果你觉得自己有那个本事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.41,0:21:52.62,OP-CN,,0,20,0,,{\fad(300,300)}那我就在这里等你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.79,0:21:57.30,OP-CN,,0,20,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我孤身一人太久
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.46,0:22:00.97,OP-CN,,0,20,0,,{\fad(300,300)}觉得还是独来独往更自在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.17,0:22:04.68,OP-CN,,0,20,0,,{\fad(300,300)}当你寻找爱时  它总是躲躲藏藏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.68,0:22:08.10,OP-CN,,0,20,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我知道你们这些男生就喜欢玩那些感情把戏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.52,0:22:09.72,OP-CN,,0,20,0,,{\fad(300,300)}人们常说爱情使人盲目
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.72,0:22:11.60,OP-CN,,0,20,0,,{\fad(300,300)}眼睛不要闭上  双手紧握不放
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.60,0:22:12.69,OP-CN,,0,20,0,,{\fad(300,300)}尽情享受这段旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.69,0:22:14.35,OP-CN,,0,20,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我不好追  但也不难懂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.35,0:22:16.40,OP-CN,,0,20,0,,{\fad(300,300)}只要给予她整个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.40,0:22:20.15,OP-CN,,0,20,0,,{\fad(300,300)}就算一言不发  你的眼神早已诉说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.15,0:22:24.45,OP-CN,,0,20,0,,{\fad(300,300)}关于你  我想知道的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.45,0:22:27.95,OP-CN,,0,20,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我知道你背负着所有的过往与重担
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.16,0:22:31.45,OP-CN,,0,20,0,,{\fad(300,300)}勇敢放手一搏  让心指引方向  其中自有美好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.08,0:22:33.96,OP-CN,,0,20,0,,{\fad(300,300)}看向水晶球
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.96,0:22:36.79,OP-CN,,0,20,0,,{\fad(300,300)}那里没有答案  没有地图  没有指引
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.79,0:22:37.92,OP-CN,,0,20,0,,{\fad(300,300)}跟着你的直觉走就好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.80,0:22:42.26,OP-CN,,0,20,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我不会主动出击  也不会和你玩捉迷藏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.51,0:22:44.80,OP-CN,,0,20,0,,{\fad(300,300)}你要是真心的  就证明给我看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.80,0:22:46.39,OP-CN,,0,20,0,,{\fad(300,300)}快来找到我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.39,0:22:48.01,OP-CN,,0,20,0,,{\fad(300,300)}“你只属于我”
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.01,0:22:49.89,OP-CN,,0,20,0,,{\fad(300,300)}这种话我可不信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.89,0:22:53.31,OP-CN,,0,20,0,,{\fad(300,300)}证明给我看  你对我毫无保留
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.31,0:22:56.81,OP-CN,,0,20,0,,{\fad(300,300)}昨日星辰为我们连成一线
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.81,0:23:00.23,OP-CN,,0,20,0,,{\fad(300,300)}今天我已占据你的脑海
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.23,0:23:02.15,OP-CN,,0,20,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我要的是玫瑰  不是危险信号
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.15,0:23:04.20,OP-CN,,0,20,0,,{\fad(300,300)}不然就再见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.28,0:23:04.78,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an2\3c&HE8BC85&}我不怕抛弃一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.78,0:23:05.24,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an2\3c&HB495FE&}我不怕抛弃一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.24,0:23:05.49,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an2\3c&HE8BC85&}我不怕抛弃一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.49,0:23:05.74,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an2\3c&HE8BC85&}我不怕抛弃一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.74,0:23:06.95,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\an2\3c&HB495FE&}我不怕抛弃一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.95,0:23:07.57,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\an2\3c&HB495FE&}再好好想想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.57,0:23:08.33,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\an2}再好好想想吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,ED-JP-1,,0,0,0,,ED-JP-1
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.67,0:17:49.80,ED-JP-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,20)}君と好きなものが同じだったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.39,0:18:04.06,ED-JP-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,20)}僕の生活はあまりにもキラキラとは程遠い毎日です
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.06,0:18:06.52,ED-JP-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,20)}でもね　苦手なことも君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:08.40,ED-JP-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,20)}ちょっと照れくさいけど
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:09.07,ED-JP-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,20)}えっと…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:12.16,ED-JP-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,20)}思い出せないことが増えていく
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.16,0:18:14.32,ED-JP-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,20)}始まりってなんだったっけ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:16.66,ED-JP-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,20)}まあ　そんなのはどうでもいっか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.66,0:18:18.75,ED-JP-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,20)}ああ　ドギマギしちゃうな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.75,0:18:21.96,ED-JP-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,20)}絶望は贅沢だもん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.96,0:18:23.96,ED-JP-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,20)}無駄つかいはやめて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.96,0:18:25.54,ED-JP-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,20)}ベタな日々にチェックメイト
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:29.67,ED-JP-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,20)}僕となら　君もきっと世界を変えられるかもしれないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.47,0:18:32.68,ED-JP-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,20)}記憶に妄想なんのその
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.68,0:18:35.43,ED-JP-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,20)}我等友情って永久不滅だし
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.43,0:18:36.43,ED-JP-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,20)}｢写真撮ろー！｣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.43,0:18:37.64,ED-JP-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,20)}てか　Why don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.64,0:18:40.10,ED-JP-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,20)}何か始まっちゃう予感
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.10,0:18:41.68,ED-JP-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,20)}ただライクに混沌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.68,0:18:44.65,ED-JP-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,20)}なんかその　わかってくれそうだと思った
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.65,0:18:45.61,ED-JP-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,20)}間違ってた？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.61,0:18:48.07,ED-JP-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,20)}あなたこそが僕の生活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.07,0:18:49.65,ED-JP-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,20)}故に　I need you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.07,0:18:51.69,ED-JP-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,20)}君の性格　無自覚？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.69,0:18:52.90,ED-JP-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,20)}伝わるテレパス
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.90,0:18:55.37,ED-JP-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,20)}この友情って一生ものかも
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.37,0:18:57.24,ED-JP-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,20)}なによりもラブ=愛なの
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.24,0:18:57.99,ED-JP-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,20)}全力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.99,0:18:59.62,ED-JP-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,20)}つまり　I love you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.37,0:19:01.87,ED-JP-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,20)}更に　I need you
