Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.64,0:18:40.10,ED-JP-2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(20,20)}何か始まっちゃう予感
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.10,0:18:41.68,ED-JP-2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(20,20)}ただライクに混沌
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.68,0:18:44.65,ED-JP-2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(20,20)}なんかその　わかってくれそうだと思った
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.65,0:18:45.61,ED-JP-2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(20,20)}間違ってた？
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.61,0:18:48.07,ED-JP-2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(20,20)}あなたこそが僕の生活
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.07,0:18:49.65,ED-JP-2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(20,20)}故に　I need you
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.07,0:18:51.69,ED-JP-2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(20,20)}君の性格　無自覚？
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.69,0:18:52.90,ED-JP-2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(20,20)}伝わるテレパス
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.90,0:18:55.37,ED-JP-2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(20,20)}この友情って一生ものかも
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.37,0:18:57.24,ED-JP-2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(20,20)}なによりもラブ=愛なの
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.24,0:18:57.99,ED-JP-2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(20,20)}全力
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.99,0:18:59.62,ED-JP-2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(20,20)}つまり　I love you
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.37,0:19:01.87,ED-JP-2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(20,20)}更に　I need you
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,ED-CN-1
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.67,0:17:49.80,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}原来我们喜欢的东西一模一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.39,0:18:04.06,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}我跟那种闪闪发光的生活根本不沾边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.06,0:18:06.52,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}但有你在的话  再困难我也不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:08.40,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}虽然会有点害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:09.07,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:12.16,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}好多事都想不起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.16,0:18:14.32,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}我们当初是怎么开始的来着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:16.66,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}算了  那种事也无所谓啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.66,0:18:18.75,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}啊  心跳得好快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.75,0:18:21.96,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}绝望可是种奢侈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.96,0:18:23.96,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}可不能浪费了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.96,0:18:25.54,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}给这平淡无奇的日子将上一军
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:29.67,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}只要和我一起  说不定你也能改变世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.47,0:18:32.68,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}记忆也好  妄想也罢  全都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.68,0:18:35.43,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}我等友情乃是永久不灭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.43,0:18:36.43,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}“来拍照吧!”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.43,0:18:37.64,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}话说  Why don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.64,0:18:40.10,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}总感觉要有什么事情发生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.10,0:18:41.68,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}即使好感中夹杂着混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.68,0:18:44.65,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}但感觉你好像能够理解我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.65,0:18:45.61,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}是我搞错了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.61,0:18:48.07,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}你就是我生活的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.07,0:18:49.65,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}因此 I need you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.07,0:18:51.69,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}你的性格  自己都没意识到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.69,0:18:52.90,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}我们就是心有灵犀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.90,0:18:55.37,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}这份友情也许是一辈子的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.37,0:18:57.24,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}不管怎样  Love就是爱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.24,0:18:57.99,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}拼尽全力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.99,0:18:59.62,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}也就是说  I love you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.37,0:19:01.87,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}更加  I need you
